text: Mirzet Kruprinac (born 6 November 1973) is a Bosnian-Herzegovinian retired professional footballer. ==Career== Kruprinac made two appearances for the Bosnia and Herzegovina national team in 2001. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Bosniaks of Bosnia and Herzegovina Category:Bosnia and Herzegovina footballers Category:Bosnia and Herzegovina international footballers Category:FK Sarajevo players Category:Bosnia and Herzegovina expatriate footballers Category:1973 births Category:Association football defenders
title: Mirzet Krupinac
